{"tid":1809771,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"為自己，為家人，勿回鄉探親，拒內地人到港","createTime":"2020-01-03T10:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T10:35:47.000Z","uid":288304,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"be6973ecbd78af0f499621863a82bdd7ed9b1973","tid":1809771,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:33:00.000Z","msg":"為自己，為家人，勿回鄉探親，拒內地人到港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武漢不明原因肺炎個案至今增至44宗，其中重症有11宗，其餘患者情況穩定，所有患者都在當地醫院接受隔離治療，目前未發現明顯人傳人證據，亦未有醫護人員感染。<br />\n<br />\n武漢市衛健委通報，流行病學調查顯示，部分病例來自當地華南海鮮城經營戶，主要病徵是發燒，少數人呼吸困難，當局的病原鑒定和病因溯源工作，已經排除流感、禽流感、腺病毒感染等常見呼吸道疾病。<br />\n<br />\n當局對121名密切接觸者進行醫學觀察，並繼續追蹤其他接觸者。國家和省衛生健康委高度重視，派出工作組和專家組到武漢指導應對疫情工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500870-20200103.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500870-20200103.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7FSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=061f1c4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500870-20200103.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4a9b9c40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500870-20200103.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c38dee9fb8d58bac08e1729a9e2a283900ffcf02","tid":1809771,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3AC0QGy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3AC0QGy.jpg&h=d2bfba86&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}